T Pumpy Concept Limited, developers of Abuja-based T Pumpy Estates, has announced a 40% slash in her land in Kuje area of the Federal Capital Territory. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839331 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0022-1.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0022-1.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0022-1-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px">  The land, with Certificate of Occupancy (C-of-O) is now N1.5m per plot. Announcing the new promo, the MD/CEO of the real estate, Mr. Akintayo Adaralegbe, said the promo is part of its ongoing Duadruplex promo, which would last till December 31st December, 2020. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839323 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0018.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0018.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0018-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> According to him, the decision to slash its price followed the global hardship as a result of the coronavirus pandemic. “All our lands are authentic and verifiable. They are all certified with C-of-Os.” Earlier, Mr. Adaralegbe said the T Pumpy Kiddies Estate promo, Build yourself which are part of QUADRUPLEX PROMO are still on. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839324 size-large" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0015-1024x683.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="494" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0015-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0015-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0015.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px"> “Our kiddies estate promo is still one. It is a package which encourages parents to secure a land for their children ages 0-17. “It is part of our vision to carry everybody along,” be said. According to him, the first of its kind innovation would be beneficial to children from ages 0-10 and 11-17 respectively. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839325 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0014.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0014.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0014-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> “Though the law doesn’t allow age 0 -17 to buy landed properties, but only through parents and guardians.” He said some of subscribers would enjoy reasonable discount on the land which has Certificate of Occupancy. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839322 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0017.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0017.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0017-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> This is coming barely one month after the company, which has estates spread across Lugbe, Guzape, Karasana, kyami, Life Camp, Jabi, Wawa and Kuje announced 50 per cent discount for its lands. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839326 size-full" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0016.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="878" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0016.jpg 621w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0016-212x300.jpg 212w" sizes="(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px"> The T-Pumpy Concept team have decades of providing industry-acclaimed off-site home designs and constructions. Whether you’re interested in a manufactured home or an innovative modular design, the T-Pumpy Concept team continues to deliver what home buyers are looking for in their new homes along with the quality construction they expect and deserve. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-839327 size-large" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0013-683x1024.jpg" alt="" width="683" height="1024" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0013-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0013-200x300.jpg 200w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG-20200913-WA0013.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px"> Corporate Office address: No. 12, Monrovia Street, Off Aminu Kano Crescent, Wuse II district, Abuja Annex House 23, (F) Road, Beside RCCG Resurrection Parish, FHA Lugbe, Abuja. Follow us on our social media platforms. Instagram: T.pumpy_estates Facebook: Tpumpy Estates YouTube : T.pumpy Estates Website: http://tpumpyconcept.com WhatsApp/call: 09054545468 or 09023333380